    " for full-range workflows." : {
      "comment" : "A part of the conclusion card that provides information about using an 88-key MIDI keyboard for various musical tasks.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    " when piano-style practice or DAW/production use matters." : {
      "comment" : "A note explaining when to use an 88-key MIDI keyboard.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    " を選んでください。コード練習や左手・右手を使った練習、ジャズのボイシング練習にはちょうどよい広さです。" : {
      "comment" : "A continuation of the \"61鍵\" paragraph, providing more details on its suitability for various musical exercises.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "—balanced for chords, left-hand shells, melodies, and voicings." : {

