    "25–37 key boards work for quick tests but feel cramped for comfortable two-hand jazz drills." : {
      "comment" : "A note explaining that 25–37-key MIDI keyboards are suitable for quick tests but may feel cramped for comfortable two-hand jazz drills.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "25〜37鍵でも接続はできますが、鍵が少なく両手を使った練習や広い音域での練習では窮屈に感じることがあります。" : {
      "comment" : "A paragraph explaining that while 25-37-key keyboards can connect, they may feel cramped for exercises that use both hands or cover a wide range of notes.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "49 keys or more" : {
      "comment" : "A phrase that translates to \"49 keys or more\" in the English translation.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "49鍵以上" : {
