    },
    "88鍵は、本格的なピアノ練習やほかの音楽制作にも使いたい方向けです。" : {

    },
    "A MIDI keyboard is not automatically a standalone digital piano—it needs a computer, tablet, phone, or host app feeding it sounds. Jazzify listens to your controller after it is routed through Core MIDI/USB." : {
      "comment" : "A description of how a MIDI keyboard works, presented in English.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
